</ul>


<h2>Disclosures</h2>

<p>
For transparency, I want to be clear that I work for multiple different
organizations throughout the year, including
<a href="http://www.hypermodernllc.com">Hyper Modern Inc</a>,
<a href="http://www.mathgineering.com">Mathgineering</a>, and
others.
</p>

<p>
I work on a contract basis for other organizations occasionally, and if you
have questions, please feel free to contact me at
<a href="mailto:chris@caswenson.com">chris@caswenson.com</a>.
</p>

<p>
All opinions on this site are my own, and do not reflect that of anyone else.
</p>

	

